```
H~2~O
.
<p>H<sub>2</sub>O</p>
```

```
mc^2^
.
<p>mc<sup>2</sup></p>
```

```
test^of superscript ~with subscript~^
.
<p>test<sup>of superscript <sub>with subscript</sub></sup></p>
```

```
H{~2 ~}O
.
<p>H<sub>2 </sub>O</p>
```

Inline attributes attach to the sub/sup element:

```
~sub~{.a}
.
<p><sub class="a">sub</sub></p>
```

```
^sup^{.a}
.
<p><sup class="a">sup</sup></p>
```
